Physicians Management – UX & Functional Redesign (Desktop + Mobile)

Redesign the Physicians Management module to feel like an enterprise-grade healthcare SaaS platform used by clinics, longevity centers, compounding pharmacies, and physician networks.

The current screen only allows creating doctors and viewing a basic list. Transform it into a complete physician relationship management experience while maintaining a clean, modern, highly efficient UI.

